Ramaphosa will deliver the keynote speech at the 4th Industrial Revolution SA Digital Economy Summit at the Gallagher Convention Centre in Midrand on Friday. In a different province in South Africa, a hologram of Ramaphosa will be broadcast in real time at the Rustenburg Civic Centre in North West. A holographic display uses light to give a 3D impression of an image. This means those watching the hologram in North West will Â be able to view an image of Ramphosa a though he literally standing in front of them.

